B^{A\times C}\cong (B^C)^A
 \begin{align} \hom(X,B^{A\times C}) & \cong \hom(X\times A\times C,B) \\  & \cong \hom(X\times A,B^C) \\  & \cong \hom(X,(B^C)^A)  \end{align} 
